body:
Hey guys. I figured this doesn't belong in media, so I'm putting it here. I finally got the chance to make my first League of Legends video. For those who play and are level 30, you might not care much about this tutorial, but for beginners this is a helpful guide. I will be showing how to get lots of kills and a huge killstreak (legendary a few times at the end) using Fiora in dominion.

http://youtu.be/iRTlZXxGB40

Enjoy! Idk when I'll get the chance to publish another video :P
